Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.65,0:00:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜歡與最討厭的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人的推理與懸疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解讀死亡訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字和記號的奇妙聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們幾個和朱蒂老師一起來到咖啡館
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然整座大樓都停電了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在電力恢復後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡館旁邊的電梯上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.02,0:01:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現一具懷裏抱著信封的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是信用調查社的社長中條勝則
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信封裏面的資料被人拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信封表面用他的血寫著○×△的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 血字找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,□
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是“口”這個字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是假名的“ロ”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據前面的○×△來看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是□
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個□比○×△稍微大一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏匆忙中的省略（後篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,○×△合起來會不會是什麼字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,□和×合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成了田字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 這個畭姓的人很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個姓很少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過繩田這個姓有三個田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 淺井的形狀也很相近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦 是形狀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 鈴木的鈴因為是圓形的就用○表示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也姓鈴木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓鈴木的沒有壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 這裏就交給我們員警來辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們趕快離開現場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏已經完事了 你去支援千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我去給爸爸打電話告訴他晚點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是千葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八層
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 警部讓我上去支援你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.47,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭小姐 有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是說總有人惡作劇的給你寫信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由美總是取笑我 發簡訊的時候總是寫上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,×××
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不問早晚也會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 高木警官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利可真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小傢伙也不知道跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 cool kid的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cool kid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是個鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴕鳥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼○×△□的意思你弄明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定正如毛利說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在用形狀表示什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 美國國防部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫五角大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為大樓的形狀是五角形的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫Pentagon
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美國 有特殊含義的辭彙非常非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White House這個詞本意是白色的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在代指總統府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橢圓形辦公室Ovail Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代指總統的辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有事務所bureau這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F.B.I
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是美國聯邦調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你有用嗎 cool kid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 剛才的鴕鳥是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是cool kid你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在電梯下面的字卻被你發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美國 管這種人叫做鴕鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思維成熟得像個大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏在小小的身體裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以為別人看不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本也有這樣的俗語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏頭不藏尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏頭不藏尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信封借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 犯人就在那31人之中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 立刻就叫人去調查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長的電腦不要讓人動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是信用調查公司的社長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人犯很可能就是在他正在調查的貪污犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去問問他公司的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有人和他一起調查
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許知道貪污犯的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長獨自在調查這件事 非常秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司職員都不知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他記錄調查結果的電腦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是沒有密碼打不開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是密碼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個○×△□是不是密碼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想才讓人敲了○×△□試試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒有打開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是24種配列組合排列組合都試過了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那○×△□果然還是犯人的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是個謎語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的猜謎節目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是用這個符號表示Yes和No
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 ○×猜謎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼犯人是猜謎王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你們在這裏等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再攪在案子裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果○×△是犯人的名字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉警官就有點嫌疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉警官的千字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住這邊就是×
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住這邊看上去就像△了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得非常可疑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮…遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的話高木警官也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 高木警官的高字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住這邊既像□ 又像○
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像□我知道 怎麼說像○呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為口這個字有人用○代替
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿笠博士寫“阿”字也總是這麼寫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士說匆忙的時候省略點也是應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏 匆忙 省略…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 千葉警官和高木警官是我報警之後才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼會是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽見了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實這個嫌疑犯的清單上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這個嫌疑犯的清單上確實有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國吉文太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國吉文太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼○×△□說的是他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表面上看確實沒有什麼聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吉和文這兩個字的上半部分遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 不是○×△嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 確實是○×△
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 把“太”這個字說成是△有點勉強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印刷體確實不像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是手寫體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最後的點拖長點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 看上去很像△吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼要遮住上半部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是遮住的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫著○×△的是在信封的邊上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來發現的□
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比○×△大一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就證明除了□以外的三個字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跨在信封和露出來的資料上面的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 寫著○×△上半部分的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被犯人拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼□呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是國這個字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必須要在犯人發現之前寫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國字就省略了中間的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 確實有這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐具上光寫外面一個框的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Great
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是從小說裏走出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探目暮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 找到嫌疑犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去樓上的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利怎麼還沒回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能在給新一打電話問X的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道了答案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 什麼把我珍貴的X給人啊 園子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問了高木警官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 要是新一跟我要X 我也沒辦法給他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對這方面的知識很不敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 柯南去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不見了 那個小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國吉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 國吉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 有點事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我們來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎紙機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,□和○×△啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠推理找出不足的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的名字國吉文太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是警官先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑這個就斷定我是犯人有點操之過急吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是被害人留下來的死亡訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是犯人用被害人的手寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.35,0:16:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用血字嫁禍於我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果懷疑我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請找出那些被犯人拿走的資料再說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會往殺人現場的這座樓裏跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是逃到外面去 把資料銷毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你把資料粉碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為那資料上有記號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新粘起來比拼圖還容易
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 高木警官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把沾有血跡的碎紙找出來拼上非常簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和信封上的血字完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些血字是國吉文太沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個能從碎紙機裏找到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再花點時間 其他部分也可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 另外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的手套被扔在回公司路上的廁所裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果國吉先生是用手將資料粉碎的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料上應該會有他的指紋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.92,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,○×△啊 原來是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大學時代的綽號 就叫做大口和○×△
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還不明白什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是讓孩子吃飽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也能讓他們高興高興 所以開始貪污
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次成功了 從此貪污就成了習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小錢是無底洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的欲望是無止境的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個○×△先生被抓住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 現在正從後門帶去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.40,0:19:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 能不能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問小蘭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 她在那裏發簡訊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…點…回…來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子姐姐讓我問小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 X是不行的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼毛利 鈴木 回家路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到收穫蘋果的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒喝醉 還能喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有簡訊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘭發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又遇到案子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是被詛咒了 我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一喜歡聽的案件內容以後再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,×××
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒戲 沒戲 沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能告訴我嗎 Gin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信有天堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定會冷冷地回答
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我不像你這樣傻…”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:22:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們交杯共飲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有久藏的雪利酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不及了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,×××
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well X 親吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅供女性表達她們的愛情…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也可以用做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仇恨的標誌…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X也同時意味著目標…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀質飛鏢射中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.30,0:23:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 滾出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點從這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什麼鬧鬼 真是白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還不是浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.14,0:24:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈屋的真相（前篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.63,0:24:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是春色浪漫的幽靈公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.01,0:24:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鰻魚怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:27.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我倆討論的未來中必定有你的歸屬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh bady I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.88,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意成為你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:43.04,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你我牽連的手發誓與你共此一生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:49.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我討厭你”這句話 即使是玩笑話我也不忍出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:56.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我喜歡你”如果不是事實我也不會說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:05.14,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在無法見面時 沒有心思顧及其他一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.80,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也被你一個人所獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:24.44,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我倆的愛分隔兩地請你緊緊擁抱著我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:31.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此心緒不寧的夜晚仍會造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:39.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時就請你給我一個大大的擁抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:34.39,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當清晨來臨我便會想起你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:40.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時只要在你身邊就感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:47.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為恐懼時間的流逝黯然淚下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.30,0:20:52.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每每出現在不斷改變的人心之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:21:05.82,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抱期待就不會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:12.66,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也別因此無欲無求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:20.05,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論前方是什麼樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.90,0:21:27.12,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夢醒之後你的人依然在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:32.62,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我的心意先一步飄向你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:40.24,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的這條路依舊沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:45.84,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然想挽著你的手中漫步其中
